_sText: A small (ish) maze in the pitch dark that needs you to use your torch to navigate. Bomb site in the centre and spawns at opposite corners with coordinating spotlights. You'll either love it or hate it (most people hate) but it can be a fun map to play.

You are in a house. There has been a criminal organisation that used to stay there. They were robbing banks and left all the money in the house also some of their equipment.

One day they all disappeared. Something happened but nobody will ever seek the truth inside the house.

This map is still in beta release. All creds goes to Xgjengen for creating the map. He did it all by himself but he has still not learned hammer completely. You can find him on youtube

I just finished the fixed version which addressed the clipping issues as well as a couple other things too. Read below for a complete list of changes. Please download it and give me any feedback you have good or bad. This will be the first peice that I can start my portfolio with.

Map Name: de_dam_facility_fixed

Author: Joe Motz
Release Date: 3/12/06
Fixed Release: 4/23/06

Number of Spawn Points: 30 vs. 30.

Also, thanks to everyone who has helped me with this map. It's been a long time coming but overall a whole lot of fun. Please spread the word and get this map on servers. Tell your admins that you wanna play it. Also a huge thanks goes out to BarnDoor for making a kickass nav file.

Changelog:
- Moved trash cans in garage so you can jump on them and over for quicker access through the garage coming from the back way.

- You can now jump through the upstairs windows. in the building. Windows to closed offices are still unaccessable.

- Added short B route to map. Too many people were boosting so I decided to make it legit.

- Removed forklift from B and replaced it with control booth. Too many people were camping by the forklift. Too good of cover, had to mix it up a little.

- imporved bot mesh thanks to BarnDoor : http://www.tequilakawa.plus.com/

- moved a light in the vent.

- added a few more props to the computer room.

- moved location of one of the opening point cameras. Looks down alley now.

- changed crate in A to allow players to jump onto it.

- one door at ct spawn leading into the building will always stay open.

- opened ip the hallway at one of the corners in the office on the bottom floor.

- Clipped random areas to prevent players from dropping the bomb "out-of-play"

- Optimized both teams spawn points for better spread of players

- added more optimizations to map for slightly smoother gameplay.

- Fixed CT's spawning outside buyzone.

**De_curiosity - Combat map for CS Source**

**Story**

_Since the curiosity rover found a lot of valuable materials on the red planet, everyone started trying to find efficient way to get there first and race begun..._

_As time flew and years passed, in 2032 NASA came up with a plan to build a base on red planet. They had the technology and really, few years after, the first base ever on mars was built. They called it "Curiosity" after the rover that found all the materials. They inteded to do just a research on the materials and were against selling them.
But mining companies did not like this at all, they wanted to start mining everything that has a price._

_They came up with a plan to send a small group of armed man in the base with two simple plans_

_1) - Kill everyone who resists and get hold of the base_

_2) - If plan 1) goes wrong, blow up the main core room or the hydroponics_

**Will they succeed?**

Map

- Custom textures / models
- Soundscapes / ambients
- Radar
- Optimized
- max 64 players
- nav file


I put over 150 hours of work in this map and I would be probably remaking the whole thing, if I just had more time...

Anyway enjoy it :)

Well it took that concept removed the traps and replaced them with Terrorists :\

Created By MunkyheaD (alias MHead) 01/03/2011 (www.facebook.com/pau.mhead)

Intro:
=======

Finally, the terrorists have entered the Counter-Terrorist Unit of Los Angeles that has been following their steps for years: the C.T.U. 

To carry out their evil plan, they have penetrated through the sewers and they've set two points of bomb inside the federal building. 
One on the main communications room and the other in the server room of Field Operations section, and then take off and not be detected or 
followed by field agents. All counter-terrorists must avoid terrorists detonate these explosives and / or kill all of them to prevent 
such a disaster.

TERRORISTS:
============

- Blow up targets A or B, or kill all CTU agents sended to kill all terrorists.

COUNTER-TERRORISTS:
====================

- Avoid terrorists detonate these explosives and / or kill all of terrorists.
